vernac_cmds: Inductive Ordinal : Type := | ordS : Ordinal -> Ordinal | ord_sup: forall {I:Type}, (I->Ordinal) -> Ordinal.

Inductive ord_le : Ordinal -> Ordinal -> Prop := | ord_le_respects_succ: forall alpha beta:Ordinal, ord_le alpha beta -> ord_le (ordS alpha) (ordS beta) | ord_le_S_sup: forall (alpha:Ordinal) (J:Type) (beta:J->Ordinal) (j:J), ord_le (ordS alpha) (beta j) -> ord_le (ordS alpha) (ord_sup beta) | ord_sup_minimal: forall (I:Type) (alpha:I->Ordinal) (beta:Ordinal), (forall i:I, ord_le (alpha i) beta) -> ord_le (ord_sup alpha) beta.
Definition ord_lt (alpha beta:Ordinal) := ord_le (ordS alpha) beta.
Definition ord_eq (alpha beta:Ordinal) := ord_le alpha beta /\ ord_le beta alpha.
Definition ord_ge (alpha beta:Ordinal) := ord_le beta alpha.
Definition ord_gt (alpha beta:Ordinal) := ord_lt beta alpha.
Notation "alpha == beta" := (ord_eq alpha beta) (at level 70) : ordinal_scope.
Lemma ord_le_respects_succ_converse: forall alpha beta:Ordinal, ordS alpha <= ordS beta -> alpha <= beta.
Lemma ord_le_S_sup_converse: forall (alpha:Ordinal) (J:Type) (beta:J->Ordinal), ordS alpha <= ord_sup beta -> exists j:J, ordS alpha <= beta j.
Lemma ord_sup_minimal_converse: forall (I:Type) (alpha:I->Ordinal) (beta:Ordinal), ord_sup alpha <= beta -> forall i:I, alpha i <= beta.
Lemma ord_le_trans: forall alpha beta gamma:Ordinal, alpha <= beta -> beta <= gamma -> alpha <= gamma.
Lemma ord_le_sup: forall (I:Type) (alpha:I->Ordinal) (i:I), alpha i <= ord_sup alpha.
assert (forall beta:Ordinal, beta <= beta /\ forall (I:Type) (alpha:I->Ordinal) (i:I), beta <= alpha i -> beta <= ord_sup alpha).
Lemma ord_le_refl: forall alpha:Ordinal, alpha <= alpha.
Lemma ord_le_S: forall alpha:Ordinal, alpha <= ordS alpha.
Lemma ord_lt_le: forall alpha beta:Ordinal, alpha < beta -> alpha <= beta.
Lemma ord_lt_le_trans: forall alpha beta gamma:Ordinal, alpha < beta -> beta <= gamma -> alpha < gamma.
Lemma ord_le_lt_trans: forall alpha beta gamma:Ordinal, alpha <= beta -> beta < gamma -> alpha < gamma.
Lemma ord_lt_trans: forall alpha beta gamma:Ordinal, alpha < beta -> beta < gamma -> alpha < gamma.
apply ord_lt_le_trans with beta; trivial; apply ord_lt_le; trivial.
Lemma ord_lt_respects_succ: forall alpha beta:Ordinal, alpha < beta -> ordS alpha < ordS beta.
Lemma ord_total_order: forall alpha beta:Ordinal, alpha < beta \/ alpha == beta \/ alpha > beta.
destruct (classic (exists i:I, ordS alpha < o i)).
destruct (classic (exists i:I, ordS alpha == o i)).
assert (forall i:I, ordS alpha > o i).
case (classic (exists i:I, o i > ordS beta)); intro.
case (classic (exists i:I, o i == ordS beta)); intro.
case (classic (exists j:I0, ord_sup o < o0 j)); intro.
case (classic (exists i:I, o i > ord_sup o0)); intro.

Inductive successor_ordinal : Ordinal->Prop := | intro_succ_ord: forall alpha:Ordinal, successor_ordinal (ordS alpha) | succ_ord_wd: forall alpha beta:Ordinal, successor_ordinal alpha -> alpha == beta -> successor_ordinal beta.

Inductive limit_ordinal : Ordinal->Prop := | intro_limit_ord: forall {I:Type} (alpha:I->Ordinal), (forall i:I, exists j:I, alpha i < alpha j) -> limit_ordinal (ord_sup alpha) | limit_ord_wd: forall alpha beta:Ordinal, limit_ordinal alpha -> alpha == beta -> limit_ordinal beta.
Lemma ord_successor_or_limit: forall alpha:Ordinal, successor_ordinal alpha \/ limit_ordinal alpha.
destruct (classic (forall i:I, exists j:I, o i < o j)).
assert (forall j:I, o j <= o i).
left; apply succ_ord_wd with (o i); trivial.
Lemma successor_ordinal_not_limit: forall alpha:Ordinal, successor_ordinal alpha -> ~ limit_ordinal alpha.
split; apply ord_le_trans with beta; (apply H0 || apply H1).

command: assert (forall beta:Ordinal, beta <= beta /\ forall (I:Type) (alpha:I->Ordinal) (i:I), beta <= alpha i -> beta <= ord_sup alpha).
apply ord_lt_le_trans with beta; trivial; apply ord_lt_le; trivial.
destruct (classic (exists i:I, ordS alpha < o i)).
destruct (classic (exists i:I, ordS alpha == o i)).
assert (forall i:I, ordS alpha > o i).
case (classic (exists i:I, o i > ordS beta)); intro.
case (classic (exists i:I, o i == ordS beta)); intro.
case (classic (exists j:I0, ord_sup o < o0 j)); intro.
case (classic (exists i:I, o i > ord_sup o0)); intro.
destruct (classic (forall i:I, exists j:I, o i < o j)).
assert (forall j:I, o j <= o i).
left; apply succ_ord_wd with (o i); trivial.
split; apply ord_le_trans with beta; (apply H0 || apply H1).
